<div id="faq2">
 <a name="faq2"><h3>2. On my Enquiry Screen the `START SEARCH` button has disappeared, why?</h4></a>
 <p>
 	This is because your DPA (Data Protection Act) Reasons for the search have expired.<br>
	<br><br>
	<img src="/images/faq/faq2_1.jpg">
	<br><br>
	You need to click the `NEW ENQUIRY` button to re-enter your DPA reasons.
	<br><br>
	<img src="/images/faq/faq2_2.jpg">
	<br><br>
	For more information about the way DPA reason input works see page 5 in the <a href="/help/Handout - GENIE User Notes V4.doc">GENIE User Notes</a>
 </p>
 <p><a href="#toplist">Back to FAQ List</a></p>
</div>
