<div id="faq3">
 <a name="faq3"><h3>3. Should my accessibility settings transfer over from V3.6.2?</h4></a>
 <p>
 	No, no accessibility settings have been transferred from V3.6.2<br><br>
	You will need to set these up again. There are also more options you can select from.<br><br>
	To change your settings click the `My Settings` button on any screen as shown below.
	<br><br>
	<img src="/images/faq/faq3.jpg">
	<br><br>
	For more information about the `My Settings` screen see pages 2 and 3 in the <a href="/help/Handout - GENIE User Notes V4.doc">GENIE User Notes</a>
 </p>
